                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:text="  Each type serves a distinct purpose and has a distinct lifecycle that defines how the component is created and destroyed. The following sections describe the four types of app components."
                android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
